=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_FBSineL_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright pure_tone sound, with square_like oscillator character around 1393 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1392.8809
  harmonic_decay_rate: -14.1023
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9429
  pitch_clarity: 89.8262
  inharmonicity: 0.0036
  type: square_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -26.9991
  resonance_freq: 1399.6582

